    easy: "In the United Arab Emirates, beside the desert oasis city of Al Ain in Western Asia, rises Jebel Hafeet — a rugged limestone mountain about 1,240 metres high on the border with Oman. Photograph the desert mountain.",
    medium: "On the edge of a great Arabian desert, a lone rugged limestone mountain rises more than 1,200 metres above an oasis city, a famous winding road climbing its slopes to the border of two countries. Photograph the lone desert mountain.",
