    fact: "The Royal Palace of Foumban is the seat of the Bamoun (Bamum) kingdom, founded in 1394 and one of the oldest continuously ruling dynasties in Africa. The present palace was completed in 1917 and houses a museum of royal thrones, masks, weapons and musical instruments.",
