    subject: "The blue-and-white town of Sidi Bou Said", icon: "", category: "cityscape", tags: ["coast","town"],
    easy: "In North Africa, in Tunisia, a clifftop town above the sea is famous for its dazzling white houses trimmed with bright blue doors, windows, and railings. Photograph the blue-and-white town.",
    medium: "Word from a Mediterranean clifftop: a small hillside town paints every wall a brilliant white and every door and window a matching sky-blue, a look made fashionable by a music-loving baron a century ago. Photograph the blue-and-white town.",
