    easy: "In South Africa, on the African continent, three enormous round-topped peaks stand above one of the world's largest canyons — a rare green one cloaked in forest. Photograph the Three Rondavels.",
    medium: "Word from the southern part of the continent: above a vast gorge draped in green forest rise three towering rock domes, shaped so like round thatched huts that people named them after village houses. Photograph the three domes.",
